@startuml
!include ../style.puml

participant "Client" as Client
participant "KV Store" as Store

note over Store
  **Physical Keys (Option 1: Entire Row as a Blob Value)**
  [User1_row @ 100] -> '{"name":"Alice", "status":"Active"}'
end note

Client -> Store: Update status to "Inactive" (t=200)

note over Store
  **Massive Duplication!**
  The entire row must be read, updated, and rewritten.
  
  [User1_row @ 200] -> '{"name":"Alice", "status":"Inactive"}'
  [User1_row @ 100] -> '{"name":"Alice", "status":"Active"}'
end note
@enduml
